gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Timberwolves 106, Heat 90
gameRecap.excerpt: The Timberwolves defeated the Heat, 106-90. Naz Reid led all scorers with 25 points (10-14 FG), along with eight rebounds for the Timberwolves, while Anthony Edwards added 19 points and seven assists in the victory. Tyler Herro tallied 22 points, five rebounds and four assists for the Heat in the losing effort. The Timberwolves improve to 1-1 on the season, while the Heat fall to 1-2.
